### API Usage Examples
### Replace the host with your Railway deployment URL

@host = https://your-app.railway.app
@apiKey = YOUR_API_KEY_HERE

### Health Check
GET {{host}}/health

### Full Enrichment
POST {{host}}/api/enrich
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "domain": "example.com",
  "type": "full"
}

### Email Finding Only
POST {{host}}/api/enrich
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "domain": "example.com",
  "type": "emails"
}

### Web Scraping Only
POST {{host}}/api/enrich
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "domain": "example.com",
  "type": "scrape"
}

### Company Data Only
POST {{host}}/api/enrich
