### Get Job Status
GET {{host}}/api/jobs/{jobId}
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Validate Email
POST {{host}}/api/validate-email
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "email": "test@example.com"
}